Wie onthou Roosh V &ndash; die omstrede mal dude wat vir die wettiging van verkragting gevra het?Wel, hy is terug. En di&egrave; keer met &lsquo;n hele paar interressante kommentaar oor die nuwe president verkies van die VSA. &nbsp;Roosh, regte naam Daryush Valizadeh, het vir al die verkeerde redes bekend geraak vroe&euml;r vanjaar toe hy gedwing is om events in die Verenigde Koninkryk te kanselleer.Di&egrave; ou het &lsquo;n afskuwelike uitsig wat vroue betref, so dit kom as geen verbasing dat hy &lsquo;n fan van Donald Trump is nie.Terwyl mijloene mense omgekrap is deur Trump se oorwinning, was Roosh in die sewende hemel want, soos hy in &lsquo;n blog geskryf het, &lsquo;as die president dit kan s&ecirc;, kan jy ook&rsquo;.Hier is n&ograve;g goed wat hy kwyt geraak het in sy artikel:&nbsp;&lsquo;I&rsquo;m in a state of exuberance that we now have a president who rates women on a 1-10 scale in the same way that we do and evaluates women by their appearance and feminine attitude.&lsquo;Simply look at his wife and the beautiful women he has surrounded himself with to remind yourself of what men everywhere prefer, and not the &lsquo;beauty at every size&rsquo; sewage that has been pushed down our throats by gender studies professors and corporations trying to market their product to feminist fatsoes.&lsquo;The president of the United States does not see the value in fat women who don&rsquo;t take care of themselves, and neither should you.&rsquo; - metro.co.uk&nbsp;